name: Friends In The Place They Love

metadata.name: FRIEND #1
metadata.description:
Hey PEOPLE, MEET YOUR FRIENDS!
 “FRIENDS In The Place They Love” is a collection of 500 NFTs - specially designed, dressed in unique hand-drawn attributes, and treated as a high-quality art piece. This is the 2nd out of 3 phases of Yusuke Hanai’s NFT collection. 

Grab a FRIEND for your PEOPLE and enjoy an impeccable virtual experience in FWEN METAVERSE! NFT holders are able to gain membership access to the exclusive Yusuke Hanai collectors’ community with ever-growing benefits and offers. 

Visit YusukeHanai.fwenclub.com for more details.
